OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FS Korea law to protect     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fteachers from bullying     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fparents                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, South Korea has passed a new law to    
OL,6, better protect schoolteachers from     
OL,7, complaining parents.                   
OL,9,FTeachers nationwide have been          
OL,10,Fprotesting for nine weeks, demanding   
OL,11,Fmore rights in the classroom.          
OL,13,FThey say they are frequently harassed  
OL,14,Fby parents who sometimes maliciously   
OL,15,Freport them for child abuse, to see    
OL,16,Fthem removed from their jobs.          
OL,18,FSome say they have been reported for   
OL,19,Frestraining a violent child, or        
OL,20,Fcriticised for telling a pupil off.    
